title: The Chaff
description: In an effort to get Teen Titan Go! canceled, Control Freak shows off some deleted scenes.

title: No Monsters Scared of the Dark
description: The Baby Pumpkins are scared of the dark as they go to the halloween party!

title: Enfrenta Tus Miedos
description: Atrapados en una tienda de mascotas, Manzana y Cebollín deben enfrentarse a sus miedos para poder evitar que Papa Frita se enfrente a los suyos.

title: Penguins
description: Blippi wonders can penguins fly?

title: Pajama Pajimjams
description: Oscar pretends to be a talking pair of pajamas named "Jimjams" to make his friend Pajamas happy.

title: Skips' Stress
description: Skips has to lower his stress before it kills him.

title: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs/Mizzen in Action
description: Crazy Mixed Up Puffs: The girls must literally work as one to try and stop Mojo from destroying Townsville./Mizzen in Action: Captain Crack McGraigen and his crew are tossed forward in time where discover the chemical X that marks the spot and it is up to the girls and Professor to send the super-charged pirates back to their own time.

title: Los Maestros Nunca se Rinden
description: Cole, la princesa Vania, Wu y los humildes llegan a un templo, que una vez fue un campo de entrenamiento para los Maestros Elementales de la Tierra.

title: A Patch of Perturbed Petunias
description: Share fears she's losing her ability as a problem-solver and peacemaker when she can't calm a squabble between a group of Whiffles and a flower bed of Perturbed Petunias. Cheer discovers it's not Share's fault; the Petunias are being secretly manipulated by Bluster's rumor-mongering.

title: Volcano
description: On a drive through the mountains, Blippi is nearly hit by a puff of smoke from a volcano vent! Curious about what makes a volcano erupt, Blippi and FETCH fly into the volcano. With some close calls, they watch Maggie the Magma Monster gobble up the floor and play a favorite game - The Floor is Lava!

title: Haunted Campfire
description: The campers must battle ghosts of their own creation after their scary stories mysteriously come true.

title: La Hora Mas Oscura
description: Los Ninjas, los Munces y los Geckles se refugian en la Cueva Fuerte Geckle , pero enfrentan al Hechicero Calavera y al Dragón Grief-Bringer.

title: Little Elvis
description: The Titans team up with Shazam in order to defeat the evil Mr. Mind.

title: TV Knight 8
description: Teen Titans Go takes a comedic look at the superheroes' lives. Viewers finally get the opportunity to watch what life is like for the super teens when their capes are left at home. The teens will deal with everyday issues of adolescence including laundry contests and quests to construct the perfect sandwich.

title: Pizza Hero
description: It's the end of the school year, and as is tradition at Aberdale Elementary, Papa Marianio is slated to dish out his famous pizza along with a spectacle of song and dance. As the kids wait in excitement, they share memories about times with Papa.

title: Franken Pelea
description: Ben se sube al Rustbuggy para recibir una lección de conducción a lo largo de las dunas de Cabo Cod. Pero el plan da un extraño giro cuando el Rustbuggy se transforma en un monstruo motorizado por Bootleg, otra transformación alienígena de Kevin 11.

title: The Library
description: The campers spend a rainy day at the library.

title: Moon Problems
description: The Moon gets sad when Oscar loses his friendship bracelet.

title: Jugo arcoiris
description: Después de desafiarse unos a otros a tomar el Latte de Pegaso de Chef, Izzy y Jude están llenos de energía y Duncan y Courtney hacen un viaje por carretera para tratar de reemplazar la bebida antes de que Chef descubra que desapareció.

title: Aquarium for a Dream
description: Gwen tries to convince Chef to tell the class the truth about their pet goldfish.

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: The Curse of Elmore
description: When Gumball's schoolfriend Leslie finds an old video tape, the creepy mystery of Elmore's ghostly past unfolds. Featuring spooky and hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Puff Paint
description: Oscar's painting is unpopular so he goes on a journey of self-discovery.

title: Pajamas Party
description: When Pajamas starts to panic that Oscar will outgrow her, Oscar tries to help but things go awry.

title: Director's Cut
description: Oscar receives a camcorder from his parents and sets out to prove to them the magic on the island is real.

title: Bucketboy!
description: When the girls tell Barry he's a hero, he takes it too far.

title: Yes Yes Vegetables Song - Healthy Habits!
description: Baby Izzy doesn't like vegetables - until they sing a song with her!

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: Time Traveling Quick Pants
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn about a quicksand that lets them go back in time.

title: Aspirations
description: The Gangreen Gang is actually committing brilliant crimes. But behind every great gang, there has to be a great woman.

title: Cosmic Bupkiss
description: A storm blocks Oscar and Hedgehog's one chance to see a comet.

title: Incendium
description: Jake sets Finn up with the Flame Princess with fiery results.

title: Masters Never Quit
description: Pursued by a magma monster, Cole, Princess Vania, Wu & the Lowly arrive at a mysterious temple deep in Shintaro Mountain, a temple which was once a training ground for Earth Elementals including Cole's own mother, Lilly!

title: Porque tan triste?
description: Steven ha escuchado rumores de un par de Gemas que todavía están destruyendo mundos. Si él no puede detenerlas, tal vez Lapis sí.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Party Popper
description: Apple and Onion's party plans are interrupted by a grumpy guest.

title: Los chicos sovieticos
description: Con el fin de terminar con sus tareas domésticas y sus lecciones de karate rápidamente, los Titanes aprenden como hacer "montaje".

title: Cluckwork Orange
description: After befriending a chicken with a bad attitude at a petting zoo, Jude is followed back to school by the chicken. He defends the bad bird's behavior until he can defend it no longer.

title: Elmore's Most Wanted
description: Gumball's dad has been revealed as "Elmore's Most Wanted" - but when the Chief of Police tries to investigate, things do not go according to plan. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Revienta Fiestas
description: Los planes de la fiesta de Manzana y Cebollín son interrumpidos por un invitado malhumorado.

title: Snow Day
description: The babies experience their first snowfall.

title: Bruce Bunny
description: When Daffy starts making up hurtful rhymes, Bugs changes his name to Bruce.

title: Un Episodio Muy Especial
description: Cuarzo Arcoíris 2.0 prometió cuidar de Cebolla el mismo día que Heliolita programó una charla sobre la seguridad del hogar. ¿Es posible para Steven estar en dos lugares a la vez y ser dos fusiones al mismo tiempo?

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fiesta Day
description: The Bears party it up with a living piñatas for Fiesta Day. Wanting the festivities to never end, Grizz wishes for it to be Fiesta Day everyday.

title: The Sunflower
description: Our Trio makes a new friend in the Creek, but when her pet befalls a tragic fate, Kelsey believes she knows how to help.

title: The Ghouls
description: It's Halloween in Elmore. As the kids go trick or treating we see what everyone in town is up to. The ghosts and ghouls are finding it increasingly difficult to scare children, and are only scaring part-time. Can Gumball and Darwin help them get their scare back?

title: Christmas in July
description: The babies pretend it's Christmas in hopes of getting Lola the stethoscope she wants.

title: Monster Visit
description: The monsters get nervous when their Godmonster comes for a visit.

title: Video Cita
description: Panda es un ávido salidor de citas por Internet, y cuando una adorable mujer francesa coincide con él y accede a tener una cita virtual con video, Panda y sus hermanos manejan la situación para poder mostrar su mejor perfil en el video, aunque ese perfil sea absolutamente exagerado.

title: Video Date
description: Panda is an avid e-dater, and when a lovely French woman matches with him and agrees to a video chat date. Panda and his brothers engineer the situation so Panda is able to show the best side of himself on the video chat, even if that side of him is completely exaggerated.

title: Twelve Angry Hedgehogs
description: Hedgehog wants to win the Golden Science Badge but runs into some unexpected competition.

title: Bichos
description: Cuando Unikitty y la banda descubren un bicho asqueroso en el castillo, están desesperados por deshacerse de él para siempre, pero Unikitty se niega a permitir que lo aplasten, no importa qué tan asqueroso o peligroso parezca. ¿Qué tipo de red está tejiendo Unikitty para sus amigos?

title: La cita
description: Cuando Chef está feliz ordena pizza para los niños. Esto le da a Owen & Jude la idea de crear una falsa admiradora secreta para Chef.

title: Cat Burglar
description: An alarmingly familiar cat burglar terrorizes Townsville.

title: Pequeno Elvis
description: Los Titanes se unen a Shazam para derrotar al malvado Mr. Mind.

title: Costume Crisis
description: Uncle Grandpa makes improvements to a kid's Halloween costume.

title: Snow Place Like Home
description: When the Bears realize whatever they build with snow comes to life they decide to build the biggest snow party of all time.

title: Charm School's Out
description: During a family cookout at a forest campsite, Charmcaster users her magic to switch places with Gwen, but when Ben catches "Charmcaster" sneaking about, he attacks, unaware it's actually his cursed cousin!

title: Hot to the Touch
description: Finn goes on a quest to prove Flame Princess isn't really evil.

title: R & Arr
description: It's Lazy Sunday, and Unikitty and Puppycorn are having such an amazing time hanging out on the couch, they never want to move! Richard insists they have chores to do, but they're unwilling to let Lazy Sunday end. The two go to ridiculous lengths to never leave the comfort of their sofa, rowing it across the castle and like a ship and conscripting their friends to abandon their chores and join Lazy Sunday… no matter how dangerous and impossible it might become!

title: Spin Out
description: Taz learns a tough lesson. He shouldn't spin after eating too much candy.

title: El Dragon Grief-Bringer
description: Nya y Kai, quienes se han convertido en los líderes de los Munces y Geckles, intentan unirlos para derrotar a su enemigo mutuo, el Hechicero Calavera.

title: Made of Honor
description: Steven has a big surprise for the Crystal Gems.

title: Duo Espinoso
description: Después de dejar Pequeña Escuela Madre, Steven ha encontrado un nuevo pasatiempo: las plantas.

title: Space Invasion
description: A visit from Puddle the alien tests the limit of Oscar's hosting skills.

title: West in Pieces
description: It's the old west and Mojo the Kid has robbed the first bank ever and forced the sheriff out of town and it is up to the Steamypuff Girls to save the day at a high-noon showdown.

title: Sin Cebollin
description: Manzana trata de sobrevivir un fin de semana solo mientras cuida la planta de Cebollín.

title: Pepper's Blanket Is Missing
description: Pepper's blanket goes missing at a cabin sleepover.

title: Historias Alternas
description: Rob crea una variedad de programas y formatos derivados ambientados en Elmore para reemplazar a Gumball.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Fuzzy Pink Time Babies
description: Oscar and Hedgehog learn how to stop time.

title: Los de Arriba Contra Atacan
description: Cole y los de abajo llegan para rescatar a los Ninjas. Para ello, Cole tendrá que recuperar las espadas legendarias, las Espadas de la Liberación.

title: New Jersey
description: After donning a brand new Jersey, JP is recruited by the Hockey Kids! The only way to get JP back is for Craig and Kelsey to hit the ice!

title: A Very Percy Valentine's Day
description: It's Valentine's Day and no one on Sodor is happier than Percy -- he gets to deliver everyone's gifts to their friends throughout the island! Unfortunately, his energetic eagerness turns to panic when an accident on the rails causes everyone's presents to fall in the mud! With Thomas' help, Percy discovers a way to still deliver the feelings behind everyone's presents -- by using the gift of song!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Understanding
description: Gumball and Darwin find themselves in serious trouble when they agree to everything the new kid in school says. The truth is they can't understand a word that he says. Peter Pepperoni has been home schooled and developed a very odd way of speaking. Due to a series of misunderstandings Gumball and Darwin end up on the run from the law.

title: Awesome Brawlers Training  Camp
description: The Awesome Brawlers head to a training facility owned by Kasami International to prepare for the Bakugan Battle League - Los Volmos. But once the gang figures out they will all be competing against each other for the same title, the "team building" retreat doesn't quite go as planned./Agit turns up at the Kasami training facility and fits right in with the Awesome brawlers. This is a lifestyle that he can get used to, but it becomes apparent Agit is torn between a life as a phantom thief and life as a brawler.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Mop Forever
description: At Alice's dress-up party the campers are magically turned into their costumes.

title: Hashtag #1 Fan
description: Panda gets kidnapped by a pair of deranged French foxes.

title: Computer Vampire
description: Oscar finds a mysterious old video game in the library.

title: Feeling Spacey
description: Oscar and Hedgehog arrive on a planet that has no emotions.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Little Graduation
description: Steven and the Gems celebrate Little Homeschool's first graduating class.

title: Rain, Rain Go Away
description: After Grumpy's anger sends his belly badge out of control with a thunderstorm that floods a newly-planted Whiffle meadow, he vows to never be grumpy again. Renaming himself "Mr. Happy," he drives everyone crazy with niceness. When the Whiffles desperately need his clouds to make rain and Mr. Happy can't deliver, Cheer and the team must get him back in touch with his inner grump.

title: Dama de honor
description: Steven tiene una gran sorpresa para las Gemas de Cristal.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: K.I.L.I.T. Radio
description: Muscle Man wants a local radio station to play the song he wrote for Starla.

title: Noticias Unikitty
description: Estás viendo el programa de noticias del Unireino Super Good Morning Time Action Information Show, un programa de noticias variadas realizado (mal) por Unikitty y la banda: Hawkodile se encarga del clima, Puppycorn habla deportes, a pesar de no saber ninguna de las reglas, la Dra. Fox tiene un divertido segmento de cocina científica que sale mal, y Richard quiere que el programa deje de emitirse. Unikitty tiene un reportaje contundente y una gran primicia después de la pausa, isi el estudio sobrevive tanto tiempo!

title: Chloe and Ice Bear
description: On a day out with just Ice Bear, Chloe realizes Ice Bear only runs errands for his brothers. Determined to show him a fun day in the city, Chloe promises to help Ice Bear have a good time, even if it means staying  in a museum after it closes.

title: The Question
description: Steven shows some city slicker gems how the cowboys lived.

title: The First Day
description: Best friends Oscar and Hedgehog get dropped off at their first day at summer camp.

title: Why So Blue?
description: Steven has heard rumors of a pair of Gems that are still destroying worlds. If he can't stop them, maybe Lapis can.

title: Field Trip
description: A group of teenage superheroes are being shown around the Fortress of Solitude when they inadvertently cause the phantom zone projector to trap Superman and release three Kryptonian criminals.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: Encantadas
description: Durante una comida familiar en un campamento forestal, Charmcaster usa su magia para cambiar de lugar con Gwen, pero cuando Ben descubre a "Charmcaster" husmeando, ataca, sin darse cuenta de que en realidad es su hechizada prima.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Familiar
description: With many changes going on in his life, Steven tries to find his place in the world.

title: Popular Banana Split
description: Hedgehog and Max discover a tiny high school when they are accidentally shrunk by a science experiment.

title: Craig World
description: Craig creates an amusement park in the Creek! But when things start to get stale, he vows to make it bigger and better, no matter what it takes!

title: Uncle Grandpa Runs for President
description: Uncle Grandpa and Pizza Steve run against one another in the RV presidential race.

title: La Tienda De Cupcakes
description: Quando o adorado computador dos ursos quebra, os três são obrigados a fazer algo que nunca haviam feito antes: arrumar um emprego. Eles começam a trabalhar numa loja badalada de cupcakes e se dão conta de que o mercado profissional é muito mais penoso do que achavam.

title: RV Olympics
description: Pizza Steve and Mr. Gus compete in the RV Olympics.

title: Franken-Fight
description: Ben hops into the Rustbuggy for a driving lesson along the sand dunes of Cape Cod, but he takes a freaky switchback turn when the Rustbuggy is mutated into a motor-monster by Bootleg, another alien transformation of Kevin 11, with powers similar to Upgrade!

title: Positive Attitude Theory
description: Apple and Onion spend a day in Falafel's shoes and use their positive attitude to prove he shouldn't be so grumpy.

title: Billy Bajillions
description: In Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max are on a hike to find the Forgeti, but when they realize they've stumbled upon Billy Billions own "Winter in July" ski resort, Ben must battle Billy, with an assist from the Forgeti itself.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Chocolate Money Badgers
description: Oscar learns that he can earn merit badges that unlock prizes.

title: El pollo maniaco
description: Después de hacerse amigo de un pollo con mala actitud en un zoológico de contacto, este lo sigue de regreso a la escuela. Él defiende la mala conducta del ave hasta que ya no puede seguir haciéndolo.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Reunited
description: Steven brings everyone together for a special reunion.

title: The Ascent
description: Cole, the Lowly, Princess Vania and Wu discover that the stone-mech is fueled by Elemental Power, and attach it to the mine-carts in an effort to blast their way out of the mountain to confront the evil Skull Sorcerer!

title: Molestando a los Bichos
description: El equipo de Tennyson viaja al Instituto Crisalín en busca de yoga a altas temperaturas y buenas vibraciones, solo para descubrir que los hermanos Bicho también están de vacaciones. Pero ¿los astutos insectoides están realmente de vacaciones, o están tramando otro de sus tontos planes?

title: Bridge Out
description: After an overpass collapses on the highway, Team Tennyson is in a traffic jam along with Simon Sez and family. But when Ben and Simon team up to tackle the gridlock together, Simon only makes matters much, much worse.

title: Sumo Goes West
description: Clarence learns his best friend Sumo may transfer to another school! It's up to Clarence to protest, petition and rally to convince everyone to let Sumo stay - or face losing his closest school pal!

title: Vote Gumball…and Penny?
description: Gumball is running for School President and is looking for a worthy running mate. When he asks his girlfriend Penny, he does not get the answer he expects. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Mother's Day
description: Gumball, Darwin and Anais need to find the perfect Mother's Day gift. Will it be a cute card, a thoughtful painting or something entirely different? Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Teoria de Actitud Positiva
description: Manzana y Cebollín pasan un día en los zapatos de Falafel y usan su actitud positiva para demostrar que no debería estar tan malhumorado.

title: Body Swap
description: Fed up with their home experiences, Craig, Kelsey and JP agree to switch bodies!

title: The Soundhouse
description: Oscar and Hedgehog discover a new structure on the island and become friends with its caretaker.

title: Perfect Day
description: Ben thinks he's having 'the perfect day' only to realize he's been put in a dream world by Enoch and the Forever Knights who are after the Omnitrix. Ben's "dream world" soon becomes a nightmare world, with Ben forced to live out his ultimate terror...being stuck at school! But with Max and Gwen's help, he's able to vanquish his nightmare foes and re-enter the real world where he takes down  Enoch...only to reveal an even more powerful knight...The Forever King.

title: First Car
description: No kind of travel is too difficult for the BlippiMobile, not even TIME travel! Blippi and FETCH head back in time to see what the first cars were like, and who better to show him than Blippi's great-grandpa Blippi! It's a harrowing ride, but along the way Blippi finds the answers he's looking for.

title: Buff's BFF
description: When Buff befriends Mr. Freeze's snowcrawler Snowy, the other Batwheels bristle at the thought of hanging out with a "bad guy…" so Buff sets out to change their minds.

title: The Upply Strike Back!
description: Cole and the Upply arrive at the Skull Sorcerer's keep in the hopes of rescuing Lloyd and the other ninja. But in order to do so, Cole will need to retrieve his mother's fabled swords, the Blades of Deliverance, which are hidden somewhere inside the keep!

title: Valentine's Hearts
description: As the other engines prepare for a Valentine's Day party, Kana is worried: she doesn't know what to bring! Inspired by Sandy's giant metal heart surprise, Kana decides that she is going to create a sparkly big heart using her electricity! Through a series of accidents, Kana realizes that the best surprise she could bring to the party is herself!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Wash Your Hands, Scrub That Soap
description: Ella is getting muddy. Mei comes out with a plate of dumplings, but Ella's hands are dirty!

title: I Heart Heartforde
description: Oscar, hedgehog and the other campers are excited to take a trip to the non-magical town of Heartforde.

title: Campers Above the Bed
description: Hedgehog finds a city underneath her bed as she looks for her missing diary.

title: Splash Zone
description: Mayor Foghorn Leghorn hires The Looney Builders to build a giant water slide for Looneyburg's waterpark. He keeps adding onto the design with the support of Bugs until problems arise.

title: La pregunta
description: Steven les muestra a unas gemas citadinas cómo vivían los vaqueros.

title: They Sent Us a Pie/Dust in the Wind
description: A giant pie is sent to Pretty Big City to stop an asteroid… but the Mechas and friends have eaten the whole thing!/The Singing Stone Heads are ready to perform at the Museum, but when they open their mouths, they sneeze instead of sing!

title: Beach Heads
description: After traveling to Tampa Beach, Florida, Team Tennyson hopes to get some much-needed rest & relaxation, but the tempests without a temper, the Weatherheads, have other plans that Ben must thwart: to build a new beach base!

title: Them Soviet Boys
description: In order to quickly get through their chores and karate lessons, the Titans learn how to montage

title: That's Not My Baby/Simian Says
description: That's Not My Baby!: The girls save a baby from a monster attacking Townsville but can't find the mother. Can these three superheroes manage to take care of one little baby?/Simian Says: When the Narrator is mysteriously bound and gagged, Mojo Jojo takes over his job, ordering the girls to steal for him all around Townsville.

title: Uncle Baseball
description: A failing little league team on the brink of giving up gets help from Uncle Grandpa and some Major League Baseball players.

title: Free Chili
description: When Owen hides a walkie-talkie inside his chili dog, Harold believes it's an alien here to destroy Earth.

title: La Transformacion
description: iLe piden a Gumball que resuelva una disputa entre Penny y su familia!
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: The Mysterious Revenger/Wynton vs. Lia
description: The Mysterious Revenger: It's the quarter finals of the Bakugan Battle League, the top eight brawlers are set to face off! In this round, Dan will face off against the Bakugan rocker - Revenger! These two brawlers give it their all in this icy cold clash!/Wynton Vs. Lia: The quarter finals continue, and it's the first Awesome Brawler vs. Awesome Brawler matches of the Bakugan Battle League tournament. In this round, it's Wynton vs. Lia and Shun vs. Lightning.

title: A Yoorg Awakening
description: Funshine's jokes unwittingly hurt the feelings of a strange Rock Giant. Disturbed from its slumber, the usually benign creature inadvertently creates havoc for the Whiffles until Funshine calms it by apologizing.

title: Ice Cream Headache
description: The campers get magical powers from the witches supply of magic ice cream.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: The Transformation
description: Penny's family is unhappy that she's decided to come out of her shell literally. And Penny wants her family to come out of their shells...also literally. They are at an impasse so who do they turn to in their time of trouble? Gumball of course! Needless to say he is way outside of his comfort zone.

title: The Biggest Adventure Club
description: When Thomas finds a treasure map he creates "The Big Adventure Club," to seek the treasure, but when Sandy wants to join, Thomas says she's too little, so Sandy forms her own club.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Pet Shop
description: Pet Shop tells the tale of where the Baby Bears once lived, and after a run-in with a video crew shooting a Sarah McLachlan-type animal adoption video, almost seized an opportunity to find a home separated from each other.

title: CN Special: NBA All-Star Slam Dunk Contest
description: Cartoon Network's version of the NBA Slam Dunk Contest, highlighting the best slam dunks, hosted by the Teen Titans.

title: The Date
description: When Chef is happy he orders pizza for the kids, this gives Owen & Jude the idea to create a fake secret admirer for Chef.

title: La burla
description: En un esfuerzo por cancelar "Los Jóvenes Titanes en Acción", Control Fenómeno muestra algunas escenas eliminadas del programa.

title: Baba Yaga House
description: Squatter Otter tries to win Panda's trust and convince the Bears to live in a mysterious house.

title: Susie's Fantastical Scavenger Hunt
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must learn to exist without each other when they are put on different teams during a scavenger hunt.

title: Los Espectros
description: Halloween ya no es lo que solía ser. ¿Pueden Gumball y Darwin ayudar a los monstruos a recuperar su capacidad de asustar?
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Saxophone Come Home
description: Oscar befriends a teenage Yeti.

title: The Spinoffs
description: Wishing to get rid of Gumball once and for all, his nemesis Rob offers up a variety of reality, action and comedy shows featuring characters other than Gumball. Unfortunately for Rob, each one is worse than the last.

title: Squirrels
description: Blippi and FETCH are going on a treasure hunt! For Squirrel treasure that is. Their new friend Sparky the Squirrel has her nuts buried all over the park and Blippi tries to remember where she buried them. Sparky remembers them all though and Blippi learns why squirrels bury their nuts.

title: Hibernacion
description: Por ser un grupo urbano, los Osos jamás escucharon hablar de la idea de hibernar, hasta que Chloe les cuenta al respecto. Pardo, a quien le encanta la idea de comer mucho y luego dormir todo lo que se le dé la gana, se entrega a la hibernación sin pensarlo. Pero está tan entusiasmado con la idea de hibernar... que no se puede dormir.

title: Cupcake Job
description: When the Bears' beloved laptop breaks, they finally have the need to do something they've never done before: get jobs. Working at a trendy cupcake shop, the Bears find  that the working world is much tougher than they realized.

title: Merry Moochmas
description: It's wintertime in Aberdale and Clarence is convinced his winter wish for snow in Arizona will come true! However, his classmate Belson along with his grumpy cousin Gary Mooch are a little tougher to convince.

title: Valentimes
description: When Clarence notices his teacher Ms. Baker is the only one in class left without a Valentine this year, he decides to enlist the help of Sumo to set her up with Sumo's teacher, Mr. Mozer! Will sparks fly or will the boy's naive view of romance backfire?

title: Cabeza de Playa
description: Después de viajar a Tampa Beach, Florida, el equipo Tennyson espera poder descansar y relajarse, pero las tempestades sin temperamento, los Climáticos, tienen otros planes que Ben debe frustrar: iconstruir una nueva base en la playa!

title: Legs from Here to Homeworld
description: Steven travels to visit family.

title: Grief Bringer
description: Nya and Kai, who have become the respective leaders of the Munce and Geckles, attempt to unite the tribes in an effort to defeat their mutual enemy, the Skull Sorcerer, who schemes against them.

title: Unikitty News!
description: You're watching the Unikingdom News Show Super Good Morning Time Program Action Information Show, a variety news program put on (badly) by Unikitty and the gang: Hawkodile does the weather, Puppycorn does sports despite knowing none of the rules, Dr. Fox puts on a fun science-y cooking segment that goes awry, and Richard wants this to stop. Unikitty's got some hard hitting reporting and a big scoop after the break, if the studio survives that long!

title: Pull Together/Lift Up and Lift Off
description: Ranger Nat is stuck at the bottom of the crevice, but the problem grows when Mecha Abby also gets stuck./Zee is ready to launch his rocket into space, but when the launchpad breaks, the rocket is launched into the farm instead.

title: Percy's Lucky Bell
description: When Thomas borrows Percy's lucky bell for a dangerous delivery, Thomas isn't careful and loses the bell.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Tienda De Mascotas
description: En este episodio sobre los primeros años de vida de los Osos, se cuenta la historia del lugar en el que vivieron alguna vez cuando eran bebés. Luego de un altercado con el equipo que filmaba un video absolutamente conmovedor de adopción de animales, los Osos por poco aprovechan la oportunidad de encontrar hogares alejados uno del otro.

title: Chloe Y Polar
description: Un día, Chloe sale sola a pasear con Polar y se da cuenta de que Polar se la pasa haciéndoles recados a sus hermanos. Decidida a mostrarle cómo pasarla bien en la ciudad, Chloe promete ayudar a que Polar se divierta... Aunque eso signifique quedarse dentro de un museo después de la hora de cierre.

title: Blippi Saves Christmas
description: Blippi wonders how does Santa know where we live?

title: Kung Fu Master/A Battle of Popularity
description: Kung Fu Master: Dan's first match-up of the Bakugan battle league is the Chinese Champion Brawler: Zhao. His opponent is a deeply focused, and serious brawler, who uses Kung Fu techniques in battle. It's going to take all Dan and Drago's focus and strength to get through this opponent!/A Battle of Popularity: Shun and Wynton's first match-ups in the Bakugan battle league take place at the same time. Even though they're not battling each other, Wynton can't help getting a little competitive with Shun, bragging that he can get the crowd cheering louder than Shun. The brawls quickly turn into a popularity contest, instead of a Bakugan battle!

title: Dinner Apart-y
description: Unikitty and Puppycorn are invited to Master Frown and Brock's apartment for a dinner party. But the two roommates are butting heads, and are anything but on the same page. Can Unikitty help Brock and Master Frown get back in harmony before the dinner party is ruined? Will Puppycorn figure out which door is the bathroom?

title: License to Punch
description: Hawkodile's caught by the Action Police for bodyguarding without an Action License. He's can't protect the kingdom or do anything rad until he does, but the test at the DMV (The Department of Mayhem and Violence) is for nerds! Forced to retire his gloves, Hawkodile struggles to live a life without punching, so Unikitty vows to help her friend contain his urge to be action-y and study for the test. But there's more to the test than meets the eye.

title: The Bakugan Battle League Begins/Riot vs. Ajit
description: The Bakugan Battle League Begins: The qualifying rounds for the Bakugan Battle league are taking place all around Los Volmos. The Awesome Brawlers all make it through into the tournament without a hitch, that is all but Dan. Dan faces an old rival in Trey, who's back with a few tricks up his sleeve./Riot vs. Ajit: The Bakugan battle league is finally here and 16 brawlers have qualified to enter including all the Awesome Brawlers. The first round will feature a brawl between China Riot and the golden Bakugan brawler, Agit!

title: Licencia para Golpear
description: A Hawkodile lo atrapa la policía de acción por trabajar como guardaespaldas sin licencia de acción. No puede proteger el reino ni hacer nada radical hasta tener la licencia, ipero la prueba en el Departamento de Caos y Violencia es para los nerds! Obligado a quitarse los guantes, Hawkodile lucha por vivir una vida sin golpes, por lo que Unikitty promete ayudar a su amigo a contener su impulso de entrar en acción y a estudiar para la prueba. Pero la prueba consiste en algo más de lo que parece.

title: Carter and Briggs
description: Mordecai and Rigby enter a donut contest to win a cameo on their favorite cop show.

title: Buggin' Out
description: When Unikitty and the gang discover a gross bug in the castle, they desperately want it gone for good, but Unikitty refuses to allow them to squish it, no matter how icky or dangerous looking it is. What sort of web is Unikitty weaving for her friends?

title: Stop That Ducky!
description: After snagging an ultra-fuel-cell upgrade, Penguin's Ducky Boat suddenly becomes the fastest vehicle in Gotham. Confident leader Bam must rally the Batwheels to stop the turbo-Ducky!

title: Billy Billones
description: En Aspen, Colorado, Ben, Gwen y el abuelo Max van de excursión para encontrar al Olvideti. Pero cuando se encuentran con la pista artificial de esquí de Billy Billones, Ben debe luchar contra Billy con la ayuda del propio Olvideti.

title: Dia de Nevada
description: Steven y las Gemas de Cristal tienen la oportunidad de ponerse al día en un día nevado.

title: Manzana es Bajito
description: Manzana tiene que ser alto para poder enamorarse.

title: Bears in the Dark
description: The Bears search for their missing box in a dark and scary cave.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Pequena graduacion
description: Steven y las Gemas celebran la primera clase de graduados de la Escuela Madre.

title: Marceline's Closet
description: Finn and Jake spend a nerve-wracking afternoon trapped in Marceline's closet.

title: Freezer Burn
description: Batman and Firestorm team up to fight their respective cold villains, Mr. Freeze and Killer Frost. Complications arise when Firestorm's infatuation for the wily Ms. Frost gets the best of him.

title: Mr. Softball
description: Susie challenges the campers to a game of softball to get out of doing a chore.

title: Don't Drink the Water
description: In Florida, Ben and Max accidentally come in contact with water from The Fountain of Youth. As a result, Max transforms into a kid and Ben a toddler, with Gwen having to deal with both of them. Our trio then must track down Hex who's found the source of the fountain and prevent him from drinking the water that will make him immortal and unstoppable.

title: The Basketball Liaries
description: With the help from Basketball, Oscar makes an impressive shot that scores him a spot on the Gold League.

title: El Anuncio
description: Los Watterson se ven obligados a alquilar su casa a un par de cabras ancianas que se desmayan.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Momsoon
description: Hedgehog gets a call during her radio show from someone who needs her help.

title: Luthor in Paradise
description: With the aid of Circe the Witch, Luthor travels to Paradise Island to steal an artifact that will give him god-like powers. When Superman and Batman arrive on the island to bring him back, they find that they're almost as popular with the Amazons as Luthor on this woman-only island.

title: Lellobee Lullaby
description: Come to sing the Lellobee Lullaby! It's nighttime at the farm. Mei and Ella are putting Carlos, Pablo, and Lettie to sleep in the barn. They tuck them in, give them milk and make sure they have their favorite in cuddly toys to snuggle.

title: The Darkest Hour
description: Forced to flee by the arrival of Grief-Bringer, the ninja, the Munce and the Geckles take refuge in the Geckle Strong-Cave. But the bitter feud between Munce and Geckles threatens to tear them apart, just when unity is needed most…when they are about to confront the Skull Sorcerer and Grief-Bringer!

title: Susie Appreciation Day
description: Hedgehog and Oscar find themselves trapped in Susie's cabin and must escape undetected.

title: The Fog
description: A new villain arrives in Townsville and gives the old villains an enticing offer.

title: Rage of the Red Lanterns
description: Chased by the Red Lanterns, Lobo seeks sanctuary with the Justice League. As the League attempts to stave off the Red Lanterns, Lobo reveals the real reason he wants shelter in the Watchtower, he wants access to a powerful space weapon being held by our heroes.

title: Reunificados
description: Steven reúne a todos para un evento especial.

title: Piernas del Planeta Madre
description: Steven viaja para visitar a su familia.

title: Lights Out!
description: When Bliss brings a new tech product to town, it's more powerful than imagined.

title: It's My Party
description: Oscar and Hedgehog plan a surprise birthday party for Susie.

title: El Ascenso
description: Cole, los de abajo, la princesa Vania y Wu salen de la montaña para enfrentarse al malvado Hechicero Calavera.

title: Apple's Short
description: Apple wants to experience love.

title: La pecera de los suenos
description: Gwen trata de convencer a Chef de que le diga a la clase la verdad sobre su pececito dorado.

title: Fan or Foe
description: When Elder Con comes to the Creek, Craig, Kelsey and JP each have a con experience they'll never forget.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Dragon Run
description: Thomas has the honor of pulling the dragon to the Medieval Faire, but everyone wants a turn as well.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Prickly Pair
description: After leaving Little Homeschool, Steven has found a new hobby, plants.

title: A Very Special Episode
description: Rainbow Quartz 2.0 promised to hang out with Onion the same day Sunstone scheduled a home safety Geminar! How can Steven be in two places, and two fusions, at once?

title: Face Your Fears
description: Apple and Onion must face their fears if they are to save French Fry from their bad advice.

title: Ice Creamed
description: It's Taz's birthday, so The Looney Builders build him a huge ice cream sundae. Porky worries about making a mistake and delays the build causing the ice cream to start to melt.

title: Familiar
description: Con tantos cambios en su vida, Steven intenta encontrar su lugar en el mundo.

title: La Comprension
description: Gumball y Darwin se meten en problemas al tener un malentendido con un chico nuevo en la escuela.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Picking Up Margaret
description: Mordecai wants to give Margaret a ride to the airport.

title: Clarence for President
description: It's school election time at Aberdale Elementary, and Jeff is once again determined to become Class President. However like previous years, he's unsuccessful in connecting with other kid. That is until he sees a shoe-in puppet President, the lovable Clarence!

title: Hedgehog Werewolf
description: Hedgehog gets bit by a cute puppy and is starting to act strange.

title: Ghost the Boy
description: Oscar and Hedgehog befriend a ghost who can't remember who he is.

title: The Ad
description: To make ends meet, the Wattersons are forced to rent out their house. However, with nowhere else to stay they decide to secretly remain at the house. When they accidentally surprise their guests, an elderly pair of fainting goats, they faint...unsurprisingly.  The Wattersons fear the worst and attempt to cover up this "accident".

title: Sneeze Guard
description: Oscar and Hedgehog must work with the witches to cure Alice's camp-threatening illness.

title: Hibernation
description: The bears, being an urban bunch, hadn't ever heard of the idea of hibernation until Chloe tells them about it. Grizz, loving the idea of eating a ton and then just sleeping to his heart's content, goes for it with reckless abandon.  But Grizz is so excited for hibernating... that he can't fall asleep.

title: Radio Silence
description: Oscar must get Hedgehog a special sandwich in order to save their friendship.

title: Duck Duck Juice
description: After daring each other to drink Chef's Pegasus Rainbow Latte, Izzy and Jude are jacked up like crazy and Duncan and Courtney take a road trip to try and replace the drink before Chef finds out it's gone.

title: Uncle Melvins
description: Legendary rock band, the Melvins, team up with Uncle Grandpa to help a young girl who wants to win her school's talent show.

title: Jake vs. Me-Mow
description: Finn and Jake grapple with a tiny feline assassin.

title: The Great Elf Invention Convention
description: Oscar, Max, and Hedgehog do a favor for Barb the elf in exchange for some chips.

title: Cena Festiva
description: Unikitty y Puppycorn están invitados al apartamento de Master Frown y Brock para una cena. Pero los dos compañeros de casa no logran ponerse de acuerdo absolutamente en nada. ¿Puede Unikitty ayudar a Brock y al Master Frown a volver a estar en armonía antes de que la cena sea un desastre? ¿Y descubrirá Puppycorn cuál es la puerta del baño?

title: The Spoon
description: A crash landing sends Townsville over the edge.

title: Oscar & Hedgehog's Melody
description: Susie holds the annual talent show that has the rest of the campers competing to win.

title: Divided We Stand
description: While at the beach, Ben discovers a new hero, Ditto, and soon has the ability to create multiple Dittos at once. These multiple Dittos can't agree on anything and drive Gwen crazy. However when the chips are down, these Dittos come together as one fighting force in order to defeat Animo and his army of replicant Stinkflies.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 2
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Teen Titans Action
description: The Titans learn that toys from comedy shows don't sell, so they become action heroes and are awarded a toy license deal with the Toy Master. But, when they grow tired of the action lifestyle the Titans go on a mission to destroy Toy Master's heavily armed cosmic toy factory to get out of their contract.

title: Cool Cubed
description: The guys need to unfreeze Thomas' brain after he chugs a slushy.

title: The Team Work song
description: Join Ella, Rishi, Heidi, and Bingo in their teamwork making the farm more beautiful and tidy. Working as a team, they do some weeding, they paint the fence and they put some rubbish back into an overturned bin. Soon, the front of the farm is looking neat and they made it work together!

title: Chile libre
description: Cuando Owen oculta un walkie talky dentro de su perro con chile, Harold cree que es un alienígena que vino a destruir la tierra.

title: The New Frontier
description: When Jake has a dream that predicts when his last days are, Finn intervenes when the events of the dream start to actually happen.

title: Shadow of a Doubt
description: Tweety sheds some light on what a shadow is.

title: Waffle Cones for Whiffles
description: The Whiffles are too hot and tired to work because their daily treat, colorful ice in Waffles Cones delivered by the whimsical "Icelings," hasn't arrived - the Icelings have mysteriously disappeared. As the Care Bears search for them, Share volunteers to make the treats. It's much more than she can handle but she's determined to go-it-alone and not ask for help. Things get out of hand and Share ends up snared in Bluster's trap with the Icelings, who help her to realize that we get more done when we work together.

title: Monster Babies
description: Alice lures Oscar and his monster friends for a tea party, but only to turn the monsters into cute babies.

title: Snow Day
description: Steven and the Crystal Gems get a chance to catch up when they're all snowed in together.

title: Onionless
description: Onion needs to leave town so Apple has to survive the weekend alone while taking care of Onion's beloved plant.

title: Nobody's Perfect
description: When Cheer makes some simple mistakes, she begins to lose confidence in her piloting skills and herself. The self-doubt becomes so severe, she decides to step away from her role as pilot of the Cloudseeker. But the Team needs her, the Whiffles need her, and she must regain her self-confidence so they can stop Bluster's latest nefarious scheme.

title: Ancestor Act
description: When Gumball's sister Anais researches the Watterson family tree, she uncovers a long history of nonsense. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Plastic Man Saves the World
description: Plastic Man feels shuffled off to the side as the Justice League battles Brainiac so he takes it upon himself to infiltrate the alien's ship on his own and thwart the villain's plans.

title: Midnight Quittance
description: Ramona invites Hedgehog and Oscar to participate in a special holiday ritual.

title: Magnus P.I.
description: There's a been a string of thefts and each one has involved a Bakugan. The AAAnimus security force have decided the only brawler who could be responsible is: Magnus. The shock of this accusation sets Magnus off to takes justice in his own hands and go after the thief himself./Magnus foils the latest burglary attempt by the phantom thief, and in doing so, discovers the brawler partners with a golden Bakugan.  Magnus is now more interested in a brawl, than stopping any crime.

title: The Secret of the Omnitrix Part 3
description: In a battle with Animo, Ben in hero mode, doesn't listen to reason from Max and Gwen, and gets engulfed in a weird energy light. Little does Ben know that the "self destruct" function on the Omnitrix has just been initiated!

title: Spell Crushers
description: Hedgehog tries to get over a crush so she can regain her focus on magic.

title: Sun Scream/City of Frownsville
description: Sun Scream: The girls get the ultimate sunburn and must try to fight crime despite their UV damage./The City of Frownsville: When the tearful Lou Gubrious sets a crying ray on Townsville, the girls must find a way to stop the tears before the town is flooded.

title: Domingo de Flojos
description: Es domingo de pereza, iy Unikitty y Puppycorn la están pasando tan bien en el sofá que no quieren moverse nunca! Richard insiste en que tienen tareas por hacer, pero ellos no están dispuestos a dejar que termine el domingo de pereza. Los dos hacen todo lo posible para no salir nunca de la comodidad de su sofá, remando por el castillo como si estuvieran en un barco y reclutando a sus amigos para que abandonen sus tareas y se unan al domingo de pereza, isin importar qué tan peligroso e imposible puede llegar a ser!
